        { "value": "extensive", "label": "Extensive — excavation + gravel base + compaction (+35%)" }
      ],
      "helpText": "Most lawn-to-turf installations require standard base prep. Extensive prep is needed for areas with poor drainage, tree roots, or significant grading issues."
    },
    {
